Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, sbezgen t-id s lxell-nni, ssawḍen-as-t ɣer yimi-s.
Lḥakem yellan d aqeṛṛuy ɣef meyya iɛsekṛiyen akk-d iɛsekṛiyen iɛussen Sidna Ɛisa, tekcem-iten tugdi mi walan tergagi lqaɛa d wayen akk yedṛan.
Lɛeskeṛ n igenwan lsan llebsa tamellalt n lfina yețfeǧǧiǧen yerna ttabaɛen-t ɣef yiɛewdiwen imellalen.
